References: git-fixes
Patch-mainline: v5.3-rc1

ECB's ivsize must be 0.

Signed-off-by: Christophe Leroy <christophe.leroy@c-s.fr>
Fixes: 5e75ae1b3cef ("crypto: talitos - add new crypto modes")
